  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether the use of a single blood sample of 1cc in
      an aerobic bottle will provide a better yield and time to positivity than 2 samples of 0.5 cc
      in 2 (aerobic and anaerobic) bottles for blood cultures in neonates.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
